A '''Radioactive Bar''' is crafted by smelting 5 [[Radioactive Ore]] and 1 [[Coal]] in a [[Furnace]]. 

A Radioactive Bar can be [[Shipping|shipped]] or sold to [[Clint]] at the [[Blacksmith]] Shop for {{price|3000}} ({{price|4500}} with the [[Mining#Mining Skill|Blacksmith profession]]). 

10 Radioactive Bars can be traded to the [[Island Trader]] for one [[Galaxy Soul]] on the last day of  a season after killing at least 50 [[Monsters#Dangerous Monsters|dangerous monsters]].

