==Tailoring==
Radioactive Bar is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create {{name|Radioactive Goggles|link=Tailoring{{!}}Radioactive Goggles|class=inline}}. It is a lime dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the green dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
Radioactive Bar is not used in any quests.

==Trivia==
* The description is most likely a reference to the often-parodied California Proposition 65 warning: ''Known to the state of California to cause cancer, birth defects, or other reproductive harm.''

